{"tid":1357224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求下大家唔可以習慣開槍","createTime":"2019-07-23T16:25:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T15:58:55.000Z","uid":40125,"like":329,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":137,"replies":[{"pid":"16ec2844e7b062410c98560fc202543c8e3d3755","tid":1357224,"uid":40125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:25:50.000Z","msg":"人係會麻木<br />\n五年前 我地想像唔到催淚彈<br />\n五年前 我地想像唔到胡椒噴霧<br />\n五年前 我地想像唔到防暴警<br />\n<br />\n人係會麻木<br />\n今日 我地習慣了催淚彈<br />\n今日 我地習慣了胡椒噴霧<br />\n今日 我地習慣了防暴警<br />\n今日 我地習慣了消失的委任證<br />\n今日 我地習慣了速龍小隊<br />\n今日 我地習慣了CCTVB<br />\n今日 我地習慣了廢話記者會<br />\n今日 我地習慣了被反對的不反對通知書<br />\n今日 我地習慣了記者第四權被莫視<br />\n今日 我地習慣了不義重議員<br />\n<br />\n隨著時間 人的接受程度不期然提升了<br />\n但 開槍？ 你甘心接受嗎？<br />\n再退就無退路了<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">元朗警黑合作固然人神共憤 <br />\n但我地絕不能忘記義士付出<br />\n上環的黑暗 都要讓世人知道</span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">開槍打市民 我地不可接受<br />\n強光照記者 我地不可接受<br />\n舉橙旗威脅 我地不可接受<br />\n勿忘上環 天佑我港</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fx969rJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffx969rJ.png&h=077ac6fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NF1pV6M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNF1pV6M.png&h=957ee032&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46aa357deac0c8c45ca4ff649e32ea81e0630f3e","tid":1357224,"uid":40125,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:26:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">36槍啊</span></span>"},{"pid":"7730eaa59fa9ccb4210ac9adca6ec002888d65e9","tid":1357224,"uid":40125,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:26:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">36槍啊</span></span>"},{"pid":"11bb9dd1a0cf5dffee40ea58eb5f5a79fb97fb5f","tid":1357224,"uid":40125,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:27:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">36槍啊</span></span>"},{"pid":"15287d9cece9fc96e44460bbfe1d3d62c9832533","tid":1357224,"uid":227441,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:27:57.000Z","msg":"真心推<br />\n香港人唔可以再玩落去 唔可以再置諸不理<br />\n你地忍心黑警繼續橫行無忌 再有義士犧牲?<br />\n推翻極權 係要付出代價 係要堅持<br />\n我想有一日可以好驕傲同大家 甚至外國人 所有人講：&rdquo;Hong Kong is my country, my home&rdquo; 而唔需要再有中國人操控 香港就係香港<br />\n<br />\nThe price of freedom is high, it always has been, and it&rsquo;s the price i am willing to pay"},{"pid":"745d6c75cd9c1bf7722bd10202520599d2627acb","tid":1357224,"uid":38793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:27:58.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"88509a8b0d7327a3ab67f08245ae38a3463336e4","tid":1357224,"uid":40125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:28:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">36槍啊</span></span>"},{"pid":"b4c3b058b927fe6fb6c57d76bd31ae2b4b108385","tid":1357224,"uid":150083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:28:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"74a2ecabd94a171511ba9ada3e6afa6a6dd46a52","tid":1357224,"uid":40125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:28:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">36槍啊</span></span>"},{"pid":"8a5ab86c25444bd4a49dfe9a1cdb9f11dcfda324","tid":1357224,"uid":40125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:29:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">36槍啊</span></span>"},{"pid":"ef9bfd6a36a06399b66fadf90223c4f951384a6e","tid":1357224,"uid":40125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:29:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">36槍啊</span></span>"},{"pid":"23f6c076bf561318eae5e31da7d0f4842549064d","tid":1357224,"uid":40125,"like":0,"dislike